The '''grey friarbird''' ('''''Philemon kisserensis''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Meliphagidae]]. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to the southern [[Moluccas]]: [[Kisar]], [[Leti (island)|Leti]] and [[Moa (island)|Moa]] islands.

